				<h1>RESEARCH AND COMPETITIVE ANALYSIS</h1>
				<p>If we were to design a music app that blew our competitors out of the water, we had to research them first. We conducted interviews to find our user needs and made comparative analyses of our competitors Spotify, SoundCloud, and Apple Music. For each application, we snagged three interviews and came up with a plethora of user scenarios for creation of playlists. People had many reasons for making playlists and just as many different ways of making them. We narrowed our results down to the most common cases, compared how these cases were accomplished in each application, and began our design process.</p>
