				<h1>WIREFRAMING THE INITAL DESIGN</h1>
				<p>Within my group of 3, each person was a user of one of our competitor's apps. As a result, we all had very differing opinions on design choices. It was interesting to see what worked well and what didn't, but also why one app didn't have one feature while another app did. It really got us thinking about how information architecture and interface design differed so much from app to app. We aimed to put together the best of three worlds into a single app, and after a lot of brainstorming, we drew up our first set of wireframes.</p>
			</div>
